# Local-only until told otherwise

For OpenHands work:

- **Do** run and test locally (local website / local servers / local files)
- **Do not** `git push`, create/update GitHub remotes, or deploy to Vercel
- **Do not** change Vercel env, production settings, or other remote infra
- Only publish (GitHub / Vercel / similar) when the user **explicitly** says to

Still never touch unlimitedvoices, chatbot, or any non-OpenHands project.
